essure, mm Hg</td>\n<td rowspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 33.75224416517056%; height: 160px;\">Lowest within 1 hr of ICU admission</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.622980251346497%; height: 40px;\">&lt;40</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.490125673249551%; height: 40px;\">12</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 40px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 29.622980251346497%; height: 40px;\">40-69</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.490125673249551%; height: 40px;\">8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 40px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 29.622980251346497%; height: 40px;\">70-119</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.490125673249551%; height: 40px;\">3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 40px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 29.622980251346497%; height: 40px;\">&ge;120</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.490125673249551%; height: 40px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 25.134649910233392%; height: 168px;\">Oxygenation</td>\n<td rowspan=\"4\" style=\"width: 33.75224416517056%; height: 168px;\">\n<p>PaO2, FiO2&nbsp;refer to arterial oxygen pressure (lowest), inspiratory oxygen concentration&nbsp;</p>\n<p><abbr title=\"Ventilatory support and mechanical ventilation\">MV</abbr></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 29.622980251346497%; height: 44px;\">PaO2/FiO2&lt;100 and MV</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.490125673249551%; height: 44px;\">11</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 44px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 29.622980251346497%; height: 44px;\">PaO2/FiO2&ge;100 and MV</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.490125673249551%; height: 44px;\">7</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 40px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 29.622980251346497%; height: 40px;\">PaO2&lt;60 and no MV</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.490125673249551%; height: 40px;\">5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 40px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 29.622980251346497%; height: 40px;\">PaO2&ge;60 and no MV</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.490125673249551%; height: 40px;\">1</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>", "more_info_en": "<p>Interpretation:</p>\n<p>In-hospital mortality, % &nbsp;=&nbsp;<em style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; caret-color: #000000;\">e<sup>x&nbsp;</sup>/<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></em><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; caret-color: #000000;\">1 +&nbsp;<em style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; caret-color: #000000;\">e<sup>x</sup></em></span></p>\n<p>where x = &nbsp;&minus;32.6659 + ln(SAPS 3 score + 20.5958) &times; 7.3068</p>", "evidence_based_medicine_en": "", "references_list": {"Validation": [{"text": "Caruso P, Testa RS, Freitas ICL, et al. Cancer-related characteristics associated with invasive mechanical ventilation or in-hospital mortality in patients with covid-19 admitted to icu: a cohort multicenter study. Front Oncol. 2021;11:746431.", "href": "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/34917502/"}], "Outcomes": [], "Validations": [], "Original/Primary Reference": [{"text": "Moreno RP, Metnitz PGH, Almeida E, et al. SAPS 3--From evaluation of the patient to evaluation of the intensive care unit. Part 2: Development of a prognostic model for hospital mortality at ICU admission. Intensive Care Med. 2005;31(10):1345-1355.", "href": "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16132892/"}], "Other References": [], "Clinical Practice Guidelines": [], "Manufacturer Website": []}}, "creator": [{"qa_en": "", "approved": false, "name": "Dr. Rui P. Moreno", "creator_info": {"about_en": "<p><span data-sheets-value=\"{&quot;1&quot;:2,&quot;2&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Rui P. Moreno, MD, PhD, is a professor of medicine who works as the coordinator of the Neurocritical and Trauma ICU at the Intensive Care Unit of the S&atilde;o Jos&eacute; Hospital in Portugal. He has also been a member of the European Society of Intensive Care Medicine (ESICM) since 1995 and became its President in 2008. Dr. Moreno&rsquo;s primary research is focused on ICU management and illness severity models. &lt;/p&gt;&quot;}\" data-sheets-userformat=\"{&quot;2&quot;:833,&quot;3&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:0},&quot;9&quot;:0,&quot;11&quot;:3,&quot;12&quot;:0}\">&lt;p&gt;Rui P. Moreno, MD, PhD, is a professor of medicine who works as the coordinator of the Neurocritical and Trauma ICU at the Intensive Care Unit of the S&atilde;o Jos&eacute; Hospital in Portugal. He has also been a member of the European Society of Intensive Care Medicine (ESICM) since 1995 and became its President in 2008. Dr. Moreno&rsquo;s primary research is focused on ICU management and illness severity models. &lt;/p&gt;</span></p>", "photo_en": "https://cdn-web-img.mdcalc.com/people/dr-rui-p-moreno.jpg", "pubmedLink": "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=Moreno+Rui+P%5BAu%5D"}}], "contributor": {"expert_name": []}, "reviewers": []}, "system_en": ["Any/All"], "cmeReleaseDate": null, "dosing": false, "seo": {"meta_description_en": "The Simplified Acute Physiology Score (SAPS) 3 estimates the probability of mortality for ICU patients.", "keywords_en": "SAPS, SAPS III, Simplified Acute Physiology Score III, SAPS 3, mortality risk, hospital mortality risk, ICU mortality risk, mortality prediction, saps ii, icu mortality, icu, acute physiology, Simplified Acute Physiology Score (SAPS) III"}, "cmeVersion": null, "md5": "16282e342ede6136e84750485597be5f", "favorite_id": 10403, "related_calcs": [{"calcId": 4044, "short_title_en": "SAPS II", "slug": "simplified-acute-physiology-score-saps-ii"}, {"calcId": 4059, "short_title_en": "MODS", "slug": "multiple-organ-dysfunction-score-mods"}, {"calcId": 10145, "short_title_en": "REMS", "slug": "rapid-emergency-medicine-score-rems"}]}